{"type":null,"faqId":46022,"title":"锁屏下来电界面和亮屏下来电界面不一致？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>亮屏界面下来电界面只需要点击即可接听挂断(见左图)，而锁屏下来电界面需要滑动接听或挂断（见右图），这是为了防止用户在未察觉的情况下点到接听或挂断，以免漏接电话或接了电话却不知情。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=170440\" style=\"width:2.8763888in;height:5.0916667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=170441\" style=\"width:2.8763888in;height:5.084722in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":137,"faqType":"通话与联系人","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1802","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Calls-contacts","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444375609000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":10,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"不一致,来电","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}